name: Time is a Healer Love is the Answer

metadata.name: Memories of you, 2022.
metadata.description:
Years have gone by. I am still dazed knowing you once existed. All I'm left with are these memories, You were perfect, bright, stainless. I loved you, I still love you. My mistake is trying to move on knowing fully well I never will and I never want to. Thank you, for everything. Till we meet again.

Goodphill, 2022.
